        {
            "title": "保監局禁止梁慧美及葉嘉瀅申請保險中介人牌照",
            "description": "<div class=\"article_content line_1_5em\">\n<div id=\"upper\"><p><font my=\"my\" style='-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width:0px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:\"Microsoft JhengHei\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-break:break-word;word-spacing:0px;'>保監局分別禁止梁慧美及葉嘉瀅申請保險中介人牌照12個月及21個月，指兩人為達到銷售目標而偽造保單。</font></p></div>\n<div id=\"lower\"><div class=\"articlelogin\">\n<p><font my=\"my\" style='-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width:0px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:\"Microsoft JhengHei\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-break:break-word;word-spacing:0px;'>據保監局，梁慧美透過盜用一名客戶個人資料，以及核證客戶兒子的虛假身份證明文件，從而偽造兩份保單申請，更試圖更改客戶聯絡地址以作掩飾。葉嘉瀅透過盜用客戶和朋友個人資料，偽造8份保單申請，更不實地接受與兩名投保人住址有關的個人責任不承保事項條款。</font></p><p><font my=\"my\" style='-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width:0px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:\"Microsoft JhengHei\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-break:break-word;word-spacing:0px;'>該局指出，有關不當行為極為錯誤及有預謀，嚴重違反保險中介人應具備的誠信和專業水平。</font></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><h2><br/> </h2> </div></div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://finance.mingpao.com/fin/instantf/20250612/1749730364276/%e4%bf%9d%e7%9b%a3%e5%b1%80%e7%a6%81%e6%ad%a2%e6%a2%81%e6%85%a7%e7%be%8e%e5%8f%8a%e8%91%89%e5%98%89%e7%80%85%e7%94%b3%e8%ab%8b%e4%bf%9d%e9%9a%aa%e4%b8%ad%e4%bb%8b%e4%ba%ba%e7%89%8c%e7%85%a7",
